OL,3,CAppeal following serious crash on A72
OL,5,FPolice are appealing for information
OL,6,Ffollowing a serious crash on the A72
OL,7,Fnear Peebles which left a man in a
OL,8,Fcritical condition.
OL,10,FThe incident happened around 3.15pm on
OL,11,FTuesday, 4 February, near Wester
OL,12,FHapprew, Lyne, and involved a white
OL,13,FFord Transit van and a pedestrian.
OL,15,FEmergency Services attended and the
OL,16,Fpedestrian, a 38-year-old man, was
OL,17,Ftaken to the Royal Infirmary of
OL,18,FEdinburgh with serious injuries.
OL,20,FNo one else was injured.
