OL,5,FThe road was closed and re-opened
OL,6,F9.20pm.
OL,8,FConstable John Money said: "Our
OL,9,Fenquiries are ongoing to establish the
OL,10,Ffull circumstances and we are keen to
OL,11,Fspeak to anyone in the area, including
OL,12,Fbefore the crash, to get in touch.
OL,14,F"In particular, if you have dash-cam
OL,15,Fthat could assist with our
OL,16,Finvestigation then please make contact
OL,17,Fwith officers."
